## Usage Examples

### Voice Commands

```
"PRIME, open Firefox"
"What's on my screen?"
"Create a note: Meeting at 3pm tomorrow"
"Show me running processes"
"Adjust volume to 50%"
"Remind me to call John in 2 hours"
```

### Text Mode

PRIME also supports text input for situations where voice is not practical:

```bash
prime --text-only
```

## Safety Features

PRIME includes comprehensive safety controls:

- âœ… Confirmation required for destructive actions (file deletion, system shutdown, etc.)
- âœ… Prohibited operations blocked (hacking, security bypass, etc.)
- âœ… Encrypted storage for sensitive data
- âœ… Local processing (no data sent to external servers)
- âœ… Detailed logging for audit trails

